snippet.title: 10 Out Of 10 Dinosaurs - Amiga
snippet.description:
This is a complete playthrough of 10 out of 10 Dinosaurs for the Amiga.
Review and scores in description.

Pros
+ A few games to play
+ Controls are simple enough

Cons
- Not sure of the educational value of running over dinosaurs
